dc_title_s: Points of Interest Lincoln County, WI 2005
dc_description_s: This data represents points of interest for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2005 and contains the layers 'InformationalPts' and 'InformationPoints'.[This feature class consists of features that represent informational points within and around Lincoln County, Wisconsin. Data was collected though GPS points, phone book addresses, USGS quad maps, orthophotos and other sources. This is a production side 'parent' feature class maintained in the ArcSDE environment that is intended to be split up into several 'child' feature classes on the publication side. Field Verification is used whenever possible.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: http://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
